@host = http://localhost:5168

### Health: open browser to {{host}}/

### Chat (requires OPENAI_API_KEY + MYSQL_*)
POST {{host}}/api/chat
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "message": "Who is playing in pro league today?",
  "userId": 1
}

### RAG search
GET {{host}}/api/knowledge/search?q=Mirage%20smoke

### Lineups
GET {{host}}/api/lineups/search?map=Mirage&site=A&grenade_type=smoke&side=T

### Matches
GET {{host}}/api/matches/today

### Economy
POST {{host}}/api/economy/explain
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "teamMoney": 2400,
  "lossBonus": 1900,
  "side": "T",
  "roundNumber": 2,
  "weaponsSaved": []
}

### Save strat
POST {{host}}/api/strats/save
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "userId": 1,
  "title": "Demo strat",
  "payload": { "note": "B execute", "from": "http file" }
}

### List strats
GET {{host}}/api/strats?userId=1
